node.text: HANNITY EXCLUSIVE: Rep. Ronny Jackson is helping residents of his district get out of Taliban-controlled Afghanistan. Rep. Jackson and someone he helped escape will join “Hannity” TONIGHT to discuss the Taliban’s takeover and Biden’s disastrous withdrawal. You don’t want to miss it! Tune in at 9 PM ET or set your DVR for this EXCLUSIVE interview!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sean Hannity on September 15, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text.

node.text: In their upcoming book, Bob Woodward and Robert Costa allege that Gen. Mark Milley secretly spoke with his Chinese counterpart in the final days of the Trump presidency. Woodward and Costa also claim that Milley promised his Chinese counterpart that he would warn them of any planned U.S. attacks. Milley has yet to comment on the accusations, but many are already calling for his resignation. TONIGHT on “Hannity,” we’ll bring you expert analysis and reactions!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sean Hannity on September 15, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text.

node.text: President Biden has been in office for just eight months, and he’s already botched the withdrawal from Afghanistan, let our border remain wide open and pushed for radical spending! How could he make this big of a mess in only eight months?! Newt Gingrich will weigh in on Biden’s disastrous presidency TONIGHT on “Hannity.”
